週。伊巴表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我退出國家隊後，瑞典國家隊便沒有了壓力，因為外界不再對他們有太多的期待。當我還踢的時候，水平明顯提高了，</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如今沒有了我，球隊水平便下降了。</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fhotblood%2F%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%2599%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%259F%259F-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BA%2586-c1301085.html&d=7wAeFZGI06oRuSpbEXG3ri7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ed45ca01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b2be9d4141dde28faf7a62db51f64e80552dbf3","tid":720190,"uid":66032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"冇左佢反而無奪冠壓力"},{"pid":"cfb4136095fe81f0a2cb30d554a7f5383329027a","tid":720190,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"伊巴=瑞典毒瘤"},{"pid":"ec6c7055297784de24a012df98bb3984f15565fd","tid":720190,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95e16a82ba4fa3bb80340aa887938d0dbc3af23","tid":720190,"uid":160934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:57:47.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，人稱「呂布」的伊巴謙莫域是世界級前鋒，他是瑞典國家隊歷史上最偉大的球員之一，雖然如今已經36歲，但他的實力還是無容置疑的。不過，就在2016年歐國盃後，伊巴便宣佈退出國家隊。如今瑞典即將在世界盃附加賽中面對強敵意大利，他們能否殺進明年的世界盃將非常關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n就在附加賽進行前，伊巴被問到有關他的國家隊會否能夠晉身世界盃決賽週。伊巴表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我退出國家隊後，瑞典國家隊便沒有了壓力，因為外界不再對他們有太多的期待。當我還踢的時候，水平明顯提高了，</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如今沒有了我，球隊水平便下降了。</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fhotblood%2F%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%2599%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%259F%259F-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BA%2586-c1301085.html&d=7wAeFZGI06oRuSpbEXG3ri7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ed45ca01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"上面d曼迷回應下"}]}